2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses Coordinated Multiple Point (CoMP) downlink transmission, which is a networking concept. 
3. cs.COMM (Communication) - The paper deals with transmission in Rayleigh fading, which is a communication concept. 
4. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) - The paper discusses the optimal set of cooperating stations, which is a multi-agent systems concept. 
5. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) - The paper discusses the concept of fairness, which is a key concept in game theory.
